
df2px 0.0.1
----------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

* Argument 'info' added to the function 'to_px2'. This sets the name
  of the column that contains the information on how to treat various
  missing values in .px file created from the data cube.
* It is now possible to create .px files with only one numeric
  column, if the argument 'measure_name' is equal to NULL (function
  'to_px2'). This will create a .px file without the HEADER keyword.
* The name of the argument 'measure_var' has been changed to 
  'measure_vars' (functions 'to_px' and 'to_px2')
* Argument 'TITLE' added to the function 'to_px2'
* Argument 'PRECISION' added to the function 'to_px2' (experimental)
* Argument 'SHOWDECIMALS' added to the function 'to_px2'



df2px 0.0.0
----------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

* Very first version of the package. There are two functions:
  'to_px' and 'to_px2'